  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 27: Enztal to Besigheim</name>
    <desc>Follow the Enz river from Maulbronn’s UNESCO monastery to the stunning wine terraces of Besigheim and Hessigheim, where vineyards cling to dramatic limestone cliffs above the river.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
